## Continuous Generation

As requested, I have started a background process that adds a new intricate test file to the `timie waste` directory every minute.

- **background_generator.py**: This script runs in the background and generates unique, randomized image processing tests (e.g., [intricate_test_1.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/intricate_test_1.py), `intricate_test_2.py`, etc.).
- **Log File**: You can monitor its progress in [timie_waste/generator.log](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/generator.log).

Each generated file is a functional Python script that applies a random combination of filters to an image and saves the results.
